would be unable to understand the temperament of a dedicated artist like 
Battle. Or how Krisel might fail to fathom the degree to which ambience and 
atmosphere weigh on an artist's performance, making her sensitive and 
demanding. But making jokes about someone's name, as Krisel did with her 
"Battle-Ax" crack, is the lowest form of sophomoric insult, and reveals the 
vindictiveness behind Krisel's article. 
</P>
