Lancaster.Admission is free. Information: (805) 948-7912. 
</P>
<P>
 A "Meet the Candidates" luncheon will be held by the San Fernando Chamber of 
Commerce from noon to 1:30 p.m. Wednesday at the Odyssey restaurant, 15600 
Odyssey Drive, Granada Hills. Candidates for the San Fernando City Council will 
be invited to address the audience. Cost is $13 for chamber members with 
reservations or $15 at the door. Reservations: (818) 361-1184. 
</P>
