<HEADLINE>
<P>
VALLEY-AREA ROUNDUP; STANFORD SWEEPS PAST CSUN IN VOLLEYBALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Mike Lambert had a game-high 37 kills, including the match-winner, as Stanford 
defeated host Cal State Northridge, 15-10, 15-13, 17-16, in a men's volleyball 
match Monday night. 
</P>
<P>
 Jason Hughes led Northridge (8-6, 4-4 in Mountain Pacific Sports Federation 
play) with 21 kills and six service aces. Oliver Heitmann, named the player of 
the week by the American Volleyball Coaches Association, added 17 kills for the 
Matadors. 
