 COACH: Jerry Kohler 
</P>
<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 0-0 04,20,05,06,05 RETURNING STARTERS YR. POS. B-T Ian 
McDonald Sr. SS R-R Ryan Sauers Sr. 1B R-L 04,17,05,06,05 TOP RETURNERS YR. 
POS. B-T Brian Berberian Sr. OF R-R Brandon Bloch Jr. 3B R-R 04,15,05,07,05 TOP 
