<TEXT>
<P>
 * Martha Washburn has been appointed director of client services at the Orange 
County office of HR Only, an employment agency for on-call work. She was 
formerly manager of compensation and employment for the Orange County 
Transportation Authority. Washburn has also served as divisional manager of 
human resources for NEC America in Dallas and manager of employee relations for 
Xerox Corp. in El Segundo. 
</P>
