</P>
<P>
 ALL OTHERS: 1.0 San Diego is making a bid to compete with south Florida and 
Texas for spring break students. Number of college students expected, in 
thousands: 
</P>
<P>
 Panama City Beach, Fla.: 530 
</P>
<P>
 South Padre Island, Tex.: 250 
</P>
<P>
