<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS: RICHEY ELECTRONICS POSTS INCREASE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Richey Electronics Inc., which distributes computer components such as power 
supplies, reported year-end earnings of $707,000 on revenue of $64.9 million. 
That compares with year-ago earnings of $442,000 on revenue of $31.3 million. 
</P>
<P>
 Results for the year include nine months of combined operations of 
RicheyImpact and Brajdas Corp. The latter, formerly of Santa Clara, purchased 
RicheyImpact in Garden Grove in April. Three months of results are from 
RicheyImpact alone. 
</P>
<P>
 Richey Electronics reported fourth-quarter earnings of $241,000 on sales of 
$18.2 million, contrasted with earnings of $34,000 on sales of $7.2 million in 
the corresponding quarter in 1992. 
</P>
<P>
 The company said it is planning to file adjusted year-end and quarterly 
figures with the Securities and Exchange Commission to account for merger 
costs. 
