<TEXT>
<P>
 Monarch Bancorp: The Laguna Niguel bank holding company has filed with the 
Securities and Exchange Commission for an offering of up to $6.6 million worth 
of common stock. The company owns Monarch Bank, also in Laguna Niguel. Money 
raised in the offering will be used to meet Monarch's regulatory obligations 
and to expand into other areas of South County, the company said. 
</P>
